ight: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tMessy<br />\n\tMessy means lack of order. What is messy? Why is it messy? What will be the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: It was messy... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) messy situation<br />\n\t2) messy kitchen<br />\n\t3) messy relationships<br />\n\t4) messy work<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tIt was nothing formal, just to grab a bite together. That was what the message suggested. All of a sudden, Sean no longer felt tired. He sent an affirmative reply and also asked about the time and place for them to meet up. While waiting for the reply, he started cleaning up his desk. It was by no means messy, just opened paper files, and all sorts of paperwork. It took no time to put everything back where it belonged; the job was done before Sean realized. He checked his phone, but the reply had not arrived yet.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/1710110881234/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912793/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912793\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p955801/\">内向的人来看~ 教你10句大招，用过都说好~</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p959859/\">老外评2016全球十大美味泡面：五谷